biography.content: Bhojaraju Gunjal is currently serves as Head & Deputy Librarian, Central Library at National Institute of Technology Rourkela, Odisha, India. Prior to this, he served as Deputy Librarian at Thapar University, Patiala, Punjab and Knowledge Management Consultant at TATA Consultancy Services, Bangalore. He has over 18 years of professional experience in Library Management, Knowledge management, Enterprise Content Management and Project Management in both academic and IT Sectors using ECM tools such as SharePoint, Documentum and InQuira. Has strong understanding of business processes, integration strategies and techno-functional expertise in different industrial areas. For detailed profile refer http://bhojaraju.weebly.com.
